<para style="q1">

<verse number="22" style="v" />Those who are blessed by God will inherit the land;</para>

<para style="q1">those who are cursed by him will be cut off.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="23" style="v" />It is by Yahweh that a man's steps are established,</para>

<para style="q1">the man whose way is commendable in God's sight.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="24" style="v" />Though he stumbles, he will not fall down,</para>

<para style="q1">for Yahweh is holding him with his hand.</para>
